reviewText:
I purchased it - hoping it was like a Donald Duck documentary - I had it transferred on to DVD-R.
I Love Classic Disney. This is just like 3-4 Donald Duck short cartoons. Some with Goofy.
Nothing about the making of Donald - or Carl Barks - or any of that stuff.
I love the coloring, artistry and animation.
Can tell it's older - with the smoking and violence etc (I mean compared to present day)
they had this vcr movie, but it suddenly froze up/no longer was working, so I ordered this one for them.  Have had NO problems with it.  Is one of their favorite cartoon movies.
